<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../../partials/head') %>
<body class="bg-[#0F172A] text-slate-200 min-h-screen flex font-sans">
    
    <%- include('../../partials/sidebar') %>

    <main class="ml-0 md:ml-64 flex-1 p-6 md:p-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto transition-all duration-300 w-full">
        
        <div class="md:hidden flex items-center justify-between mb-8 pb-4 border-b border-slate-800">
            <button onclick="window.toggleSidebar()" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white focus:outline-none p-1">
                <i class="ri-menu-line text-2xl"></i>
            </button>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold italic text-blue-500 tracking-wider">IDEATE</span>
            <div class="w-8"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-400">Your trust is our most valuable asset. Here is how we protect it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 mb-10 md:mb-16">
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl">
                <i class="ri-database-2-line text-3xl text-blue-400 mb-4 inline-block"></i>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">What We Collect</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Basic info like email, username, and the content (ideas, comments) you voluntarily post.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl">
                <i class="ri-lock-2-line text-3xl text-green-400 mb-4 inline-block"></i>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">How We Protect It</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Industry-standard encryption (BCrypt) for passwords and secure SSL connections.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl">
                <i class="ri-share-forward-line text-3xl text-purple-400 mb-4 inline-block"></i>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Data Sharing</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">We do NOT sell your personal data. We only share anonymized stats for analytics.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10 space-y-8 md:space-y-10 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>To provide the Ideate service, we collect the following:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-400">
                    <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Display name, email address, and encrypted password.</li>
                    <li><strong>User Content:</strong> Ideas, descriptions, comments, and images you upload.</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Logs on how you interact with the site (views, clicks) to improve performance.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
                <p>We use your information strictly to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-400">
                    <li>Provide, operate, and maintain the platform.</li>
                    <li>Improve user experience and personalize content (e.g., your feed).</li>
                    <li>Send important updates regarding your account or security.</li>
                    <li>Prevent fraud and ensure community safety.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">3. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
                <p>We use minimal cookies (session tokens) solely to keep you logged in and remember your theme preferences (Dark/Light mode). We do not use invasive third-party tracking cookies.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the right to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-slate-400">
                    <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
                    <li>Request correction of inaccurate data (via Settings).</li>
                    <li>Request deletion of your account and all associated data ("Right to be Forgotten").</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">5. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data rights, please contact our Data Protection Officer at <a href="mailto:privacy@ideate.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">privacy@ideate.com</a>.</p>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        window.toggleSidebar = function() {
            const sidebar = document.getElementById('mobileSidebar');
            if (sidebar) {
                if (sidebar.classList.contains('-translate-x-full')) {
                    sidebar.classList.remove('-translate-x-full');
                } else {
                    sidebar.classList.add('-translate-x-full');
                }
            }
        };

        // Close sidebar if clicked outside
        document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            const sidebar = document.getElementById('mobileSidebar');
            const menuBtn = e.target.closest('button[onclick="window.toggleSidebar()"]');
            
            if (window.innerWidth < 768 && sidebar && !sidebar.contains(e.target) && !menuBtn && !sidebar.classList.contains('-translate-x-full')) {
                sidebar.classList.add('-translate-x-full');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>